  "contentHtml": "<h1>PHP Math</h1>\n<p>PHP comes with a set of math functions.</p>\n<h2>pi()</h2>\n<p>Returns the value of pi.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n    echo(pi());\n?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>min() and max()</h2>\n<p>Finds the min and max in a list of arguments.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n    echo(min(0, 2, 1, 100));\n    echo(min(-2, -100, -3, -1));\n?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>abs()</h2>\n<p>Finds the absolute value of a number.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n    echo(abs(-6.2));\n?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>sqrt()</h2>\n<p>Finds the square root of a number.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n    echo(sqrt(16));\n?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>round()</h2>\n<p>Rounds a floating-point number to its nearest integer.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n    echo(round(0.3));\n    echo(round(0.8));\n?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>rand()</h2>\n<p>Generates a random number.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">html</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php\n    echo(rand(10, 100));\n?></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">body</span>></span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&#x3C;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">html</span>></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>You can provide a min and max value with the parameters:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>rand(min, max);</li>\n</ul>",
